<div class="PageHeadline">
<h1>Please log in</h1>
</div>
<div class="ArticleText"><main>
You must be logged in to submit events to the LWN.net
       calendar.  Please log in to continue this process:
       <p>
       <blockquote>
       <form action="https://lwn.net/Login/" method="post" name="loginform">
           <table class="Form">
            <tr><td><b><label for="username">Username</label></b></td><td><input type="text" name="uname" value="" size="20" id="username" /></td></tr>
 <tr><td><b><label for="password">Password</label></b></td><td><input type="password" name="pword" size="20" id="password" /></td></tr>
 <tr><td><b><input type="hidden" name="target" value="/Calendar/LSFMM" /></b></td><td><input type="submit" name="submit" value="Log in" /></td></tr>
</table></form>
          <script type="text/javascript">
          <!--
          document.loginform.Username.focus();
          // -->
          </script>
          
       </blockquote>
       <p>
       If you do not have an LWN account, you may <a
       href="/Login/newaccount">create one</a> for free.
       
</main></div> <!-- ArticleText -->
